"{\"uid\": \"religionnews.com-2024-07-29-bishops-accuse-olympics-of-anti-catholicism\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"(RNS) - Catholic bishops have called the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympics anti-Christian because of a drag-queen tableau reminiscent of Leonardo da Vinci's \\\"Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9998984658654222, \"rank\": 0.00010151909565381063, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.90364847530848e-20, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 57}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 61, \"to\": 79}, {\"ngram\": \"a drag-queen tableau\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The depiction was a brief episode in an otherwise spectacular ceremony that has received universal praise.\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The depiction\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"a brief episode\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 210}, {\"ngram\": \"an otherwise spectacular ceremony\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"universal praise\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Catholic critics saw this as another example of how Christians, especially Catholics, are open season for attacks by liberal elites.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 289, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9998984658654222, \"rank\": 0.00010151